  "detailed_description": "<h1>MORE FROM US</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Step into Terry’s flip flops in this short and delightfully sweet adventure of self-discovery as he uncovers what it means to be an inhabitant of <strong>✨Sprankelwater✨</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238040/extras/188894914eae93bddf834742cda1819c.poster.avif?t=1772451908\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238040/extras/188894914eae93bddf834742cda1819c.webm?t=1772451908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238040/extras/188894914eae93bddf834742cda1819c.mp4?t=1772451908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a densely packed, tiny open world town at any pace and in any way you like. Slow, fast, by foot, by car, by paraglider! It’s up to you.<br></li><li>Uncover a wholesome story through hilarious interactions with weird Sprankelwaterians.<br></li><li>Collect TURBO JUNK and upgrade the boost capacity of Terry’s very own car.<br></li><li>Catch insects, dig holes, destroy cars, become rich, wear hats.<br></li><li>Listen to a joyful and heart-warming soundtrack from the composer of Wuppo.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238040/extras/89e81298e62e6a4917bc56ffb2474efe.poster.avif?t=1772451908\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238040/extras/89e81298e62e6a4917bc56ffb2474efe.webm?t=1772451908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Step into Terry’s flip flops in this short and delightfully sweet adventure of self-discovery as he uncovers what it means to be an inhabitant of <strong>✨Sprankelwater✨</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238040/extras/188894914eae93bddf834742cda1819c.poster.avif?t=1772451908\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238040/extras/188894914eae93bddf834742cda1819c.webm?t=1772451908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238040/extras/188894914eae93bddf834742cda1819c.mp4?t=1772451908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a densely packed, tiny open world town at any pace and in any way you like. Slow, fast, by foot, by car, by paraglider! It’s up to you.<br></li><li>Uncover a wholesome story through hilarious interactions with weird Sprankelwaterians.<br></li><li>Collect TURBO JUNK and upgrade the boost capacity of Terry’s very own car.<br></li><li>Catch insects, dig holes, destroy cars, become rich, wear hats.<br></li><li>Listen to a joyful and heart-warming soundtrack from the composer of Wuppo.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238040/extras/89e81298e62e6a4917bc56ffb2474efe.poster.avif?t=1772451908\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238040/extras/89e81298e62e6a4917bc56ffb2474efe.webm?t=1772451908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
